1.0.0.name: wordpress/soundst-feedwire
1.0.0.description: The Sound Strategies FeedWire plugin fetches content from multiple feeds and allows the administrator to select which headlines appear on the “Wire”. The wire can be presented as either a widget or by using the short-code [soundstfeedwire] on a page.
